# GitHub Webhook Configuration
# The secret key used to validate webhook signatures from GitHub
# Generate this in GitHub repository settings: Settings > Webhooks > Edit
# The webhook should send X-Hub-Signature-256 header with HMAC-SHA256(secret, body)
GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your-webhook-secret-here

